name: Butterfly Pom Collection: Sky Blue | Cerise | Lavender | Parade Blue | Apricot | Kelly Green
description:
A beautiful collection of tissue paper pom poms that seems to float in an air of lightness and whimsy during ceremonies and receptions alike. 

Hang from ceilings, chandeliers and trees at outdoor weddings + bridal + baby showers + graduations + birthday parties + home decor + store + window displays + photo shoots. Use them as table centerpieces or simply string together to make perfect wedding day aisle runners or garlands. Gorgeous when grouped in clusters to make beautiful mobiles for room or nursery decor.

The Butterfly Collection includes poms of mixed sizes in S, M, L ranging from ten to sixteen inches in diameter. Set includes plenty of clear string for hanging and instructions for easy blossoming.

Available in: 
Set of 10 poms | with clear string 
Set of 20 poms | with clear string 
Custom set | contact us for details

Handmade in the USA

name: Garland Pom Collection: French Vanilla | Buttercup | Apricot
description:
Beautiful and whimsical tissue paper garlands make perfect decor for all events and spaces including rustic + vintage weddings + bridal + baby showers + birthday parties + graduations + room + nursery decor. 

Garland poms are four to five inches in diameter and attached with a wire loop for easy hanging. Set includes plenty of all-natural jute twine for stinging which can be cut to customize your desired garland length. Ships with instructions for easy blossoming.
